snippet.title: The Truth About Meghan Markle's Ex-Husband Is Pretty Clear Now
snippet.description:
People who can’t get enough of the Prince Harry and Meghan Markle story probably know that Markle was married before she met the prince, but most likely, there is still a lot they don’t know about her ex-husband, Trevor Engelson.

The TV producer was in a relationship with Markle for a long time, even though their marriage itself only lasted two years. What went wrong between the couple, and what has Engelson been up to in recent years?

For a time, it looked like there would be a sitcom inspired by his life, but nothing came of it, so let’s take a look at the truth about Meghan Markle’s ex-husband, Trevor Engelson.
